Serge Normant Meta Revive Volumizing Dry Shampoo - Imported (60 ml) Price: Rs.3300

Serge Normant Meta Revive Volumizing Dry Shampoo 2 fl oz. A super-boosting and root thickening volumizing Dry Shampoo spray which effortlessly refreshes and invigorates the scalp and hair. Use between shampoos to add texture and vibrant body or as a quick fix during the day. Can also be used on freshly washed hair to boost volume. Formulated with cedar bark extract from the mountains of Morocco clarifies to leave hair feeling balanced and restored not stiff or sticky. Meta Revive Dry Shampoo has the least amount of powder for a dry shampoo to ensure that all hair colors can use without heavy powder deposits.
